The NBA has a stacked week of matchups including the Nets taking on the Sixers & The Lakers taking on the Jazz. The boys break them down on this weeks WHAT'S BURNIN' and answer your fan questios. Plus, they discuss the hot play of Gary Trent Jr. and the Grizzlies.
